Onyeisiala Naijirịa bụ Muhammadu Buhari etinyela Major General Farouk Yahaya dịka onyeisi ọhụrụ nke ndị agha Naijirịa.
Onye na-ahụ maka mgbasa ozi ndi agha Naijirịa bụ Onyema Nwachukwu kwuru nke a n'akwụkwọ ozi ọ depụtara n'ụbọchị Tọzde, abalị iri abụọ na asaa nke ọnwa Mee afọ 2021.

Tupu e mee ya onyeisi ndị agha, Yahaya bụbu onye na-achịkọta Division 1 nke ndị agha Naijirịa ma bụrụkwa onye na-achikọta 'Counter Terrorism Counter Insurgency' nke ndị agha na mpaghara ugwu nke a kpọrọ operation Hadin Kai.
) Ọ bụ onye obodo Bodinga nke dị na Sokoto Steeti
) A mụrụ ya n'ụbọchị ise nke ọnwa Jenuwarị afọ 1966
) Ọ bụ onye alakụba
) Ọ gụrụ akwụkwọ ma nweta asambodo 'Bachelor of Arts nke History, na M.SC International Affairs and Diplomacy
) Ọ bụ n'afọ 1985 ka o bidoro ọzụzụ dịka onye agha ala Naijirịa
) Lee etu o siri gbagote bụrụ Major General
Lieutenant - 27 Sepụtember 1990
Captain - 27 Sepụtemba 1994
Major - 27 Sepụtemba 1998
Lieutenant Colonel - 27 Sepụtemba 2003
Colonel - 27 Sepụtemba 2008
Brigadier General - 27 Sepụtemba 2013
Major General - 27 Sepụtemba 2017
) Ọ ritela nturuugo iri abụọ dịka onye agha nke gụnyere 'Field Command Medal' na 'Golden Jubilee Medal'.
) Ọ na-asụ asụsụ Bekee, Awụsa, Arabic na Spanish
) Ọ na-amasị ya ịgụ akwụkwọ, ịme njem, ịma njakịrị na ige egwu ndị Naijirịa.
) Ọ lụrụ nwaanyị ma nwee ụmu anọ
